<header>
	
		
		In Part 1 of the test, you will be giving opinions and information about yourself. Look at Dimitris talking and listen to what information you can pick up about him.
</header>
	
<section id="body">
	<video class="rightFloat" src="../Media/Unit010_e2.flv" mode="1" id="1003"  /><br/><ol id="questionList"><br/><li id="1">What is his nationality?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q1" >Albanian</a></li><li><a id="q2" >Afghan</a></li><li><a id="q3" >Athenian</a></li><li><a id="q4" >Greek</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="2">Does he work or study?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q5" >he works part time</a></li><li><a id="q6" >he is a university student</a></li><li><a id="q7" >he is studying to prepare for university</a></li><li><a id="q8" >he works full-time</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="3">Why does he want to follow one particular course of study?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q9" >he wants to be an athlete</a></li><li><a id="q10" >he wants to help athletes do better</a></li><li><a id="q11" >he wants to help old people get better</a></li><li><a id="q12" >he wants to help injured athletes</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="4">How does Dimitris prefer to study?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q13" >from books</a></li><li><a id="q14" >by asking questions</a></li><li><a id="q15" >from lectures</a></li><li><a id="q16" >through doing</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="5">What interests him most about physiotherapy?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q17" >the anatomy of the body</a></li><li><a id="q18" >what to do about the injury</a></li><li><a id="q19" >the different types of injury</a></li><li><a id="q20" >how the athletes hurt themselves</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="6">How will his studies affect his life?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q21" >he will get a good job</a></li><li><a id="q22" >he will live with sportsmen </a></li><li><a id="q23" >he will have a lot to do with sport</a></li><li><a id="q24" >he will heal people</a></li></ol><br/></li></ol>
